column1: This is by far the most unprofessional and irresponsible app I have ever used. I placed an order, it was accepted, but the food was never delivered. When I called the delivery boy, he simply dropped the call. I tried reaching the helpline, but no one ever picked up. To make things worse, the app did not cancel my order, did not notify me, and left me completely in the dark. The entire day passed without any response. This is not a one-time issue‚Äîit has happened to me multiple times.
